                  <join result="persNameOccupation" targOrder="Y" targets="t18001029-13-victim134 t18001029-13-viclabel74"></join>, in Fore-street; I am responsible for the loaves that I take out: On the 24th of September, I saw the prisoner take four loaves out of my basket, in <placeName id="t18001029-13-crimeloc75">Jewin-street</placeName>
                  <interp inst="t18001029-13-crimeloc75" type="placeName" value="Jewin-street"></interp>
                  <interp inst="t18001029-13-crimeloc75" type="type" value="crimeLocation"></interp>
                  <join result="offencePlace" targOrder="Y" targets="t18001029-13-off71 t18001029-13-crimeloc75"></join>, I had left the basket to serve some customers; I ran up to the prisoner as fast as I was able, and laid hold of him; he had the loaves in his arms, and I made him carry them home to my master.</p>

               <p>Q. Are you sure you saw him take them out of the basket? - A. Yes, I am.</p>

               <p>
            
                  <persName id="t18001029-13-person139">
                  GEORGE 
                  KILKIN
               <interp inst="t18001029-13-person139" type="surname" value="KILKIN"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18001029-13-person139" type="given" value="GEORGE"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18001029-13-person139" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                  </persName>
             sworn. - I am a constable: I took charge of the prisoner; that is all I know of it.</p>

               <p>Prisoner's defence. I had been five weeks out of work, and could not get any to do, I had not had a bit of bread for three days before; I went to take one loaf, and there were four stuck together.</p>

               <p>Court. (To Gale.) Q. Were these four loaves united? - A. Yes, they were; there were loose loaves in the basket besides; these were at the bottom of the basket. <rs id="t18001029-13-verdict76" type="verdictDescription">
                     <interp inst="t18001029-13-verdict76" type="verdictCategory" value="guilty"></interp>
               GUILTY
            </rs>. (Aged 59.)</p>

